title: Holland and Barrett - The Oracle Centre
description: Part of the national chain. Stocks the usual range of health foods, natural beauty products, supplements, etc. Also has 'pick and mix' snacks, an oils & vinegars station and a large sports nutrition section. A chilled section has VegiDeli, Violife, Sheese, Fry's, Tofurkey, etc.
streetAddress: Unit 29a, Upper Mall, The Oracle Centre
